{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"opacityActiveIndicatorCustom"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"OpacitySemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic07OpacityB5Tokena"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider\/opacityactiveindicatorcustom"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token opacities.opaque","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"opacityActiveIndicatorCustom","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OpacitySemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic07OpacityB5Tokena"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeBarComponentTokensProviderC28opacityActiveIndicatorCustomSdvp","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"opacityActiveIndicatorCustom"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/opacityActiveIndicatorCustom","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBarComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BarComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and effects (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllEffectSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider/opacityActiveIndicatorCustom":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/opacityActiveIndicatorCustom","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"opacityActiveIndicatorCustom","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OpacitySemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic07OpacityB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token opacities.opaque","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider\/opacityactiveindicatorcustom","kind":"symbol","title":"opacityActiveIndicatorCustom"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_ora